descmd: This STU Update to version 6.0.0 of US Core is published for review by the public per the HL7 STU update process. The resolution of these change has been agreed to and voted on by the members of the HL7 International Cross-Group Projects work group. - see the [Change Notes](http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/STU6/changes.html).
